Looking for a Worldclass Online Logistics Management Experience?

OFFER YOUR OWN PRICE
Introducing our innovative VLIFT delivery application for bike and truck booking service, where users have the power to offer their own price to drivers for delivery services.

Users can input their desired price for the delivery service. Drivers registered on the platform receive notifications of available delivery requests along with the user’s offered price. 


DRIVER GOING TO HOME
Whenever a truck driver is nearing the end of their shift, they can update their availability status in the app. Delivery requests originating from nearby locations with destinations along the driver’s route home or nearby will be automatically assigned to them. The driver retains the option to accept or decline these delivery assignments based on their convenience and workload.

